<D>__{at least i'm paid to be here.}
<A>__{pedro smiles as he paddles away from corey, starting to enjoy his morning swim. a payphone hanging on the pool house starts ringing. corey drops the vacuum and runs toward the payphone. in the background a number of enormous sand filters groan loudly.}
